### ForgeUI / ESP32-P4 UI Studio Extensions

ESP32-P4 UI Studio heavily extends and adapts the upstream editor engine toward:

* embedded touchscreen workflows
* ESP32-P4 deployment tooling
* LVGL-oriented UI generation
* coordinate-based embedded layouts
* fixed-screen HMI workflows
* automated firmware deployment pipelines

The original upstream MIT license and author attributions are fully preserved.

All ForgeUI / ESP32-P4 UI Studio-specific modifications are currently distributed under the same MIT license unless otherwise noted.

