### 🚀 Search-Optimised Feature Extensions
The **ESP32-P4 UI Studio** platform heavily extends, alters, and optimizes the upstream core codebase specifically for low-level electronics and screen design workflows:

* **ESP32-P4 UI Design Pipeline:** Built-in automation targeting the high-performance ESP32-P4 hardware baseline.
* **LVGL Code Generation & Export Workflows:** Direct C-code parsing and array mapping for LVGL v9 visual applications.
* **Automated ESP32-P4 Deployment Tooling:** Integrated Web Serial and local compilation execution utilities for one-click hardware flashing.
* **Fixed-Screen HMI Design Surfaces:** Rigid workspace layouts purpose-built for dedicated touchscreen kiosks and industrial dashboards.
* **Coordinate-Based Embedded UI Workflows:** Drop-in, pixel-absolute element tracking that strips away responsive web layout rules for direct static memory rendering.

The original upstream MIT license and author attributions are fully preserved. All custom modifications and unique ForgeUI / ESP32-P4 UI Studio-specific core code are distributed under the same open-source **MIT License** parameters.

